ons.custom-liquid.presets.name","settings":{"custom_liquid":"<section class=\"viora-testimonials-section\">\n  <div class=\"viora-testimonials-container\">\n\n    <div class=\"viora-testimonials-header\">\n      <p class=\"viora-testimonials-eyebrow\">REAL FIRST IMPRESSIONS<\/p>\n      <h2>What Our Early Tasters Are Saying<\/h2>\n      <p>\n        First feedback from tasting rounds as we perfect Viora’s smooth,\n        high-protein Vietnamese-style yogurt.\n      <\/p>\n    <\/div>\n\n    <div class=\"viora-testimonials-grid\">\n\n      <article class=\"viora-testimonial-card\">\n        <div class=\"viora-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n\n        <p class=\"viora-quote\">\n          “Creamy, smooth, and high-protein without the chalky taste. It feels like a treat.”\n        <\/p>\n\n        <div class=\"viora-review-footer\">\n          <div class=\"viora-reviewer\">\n            <div class=\"viora-face-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\">\n                <circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"32\" class=\"face-bg\"\/>\n                <circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"24\" r=\"9.5\" class=\"face-head\"\/>\n                <path d=\"M14 54c3.2-10.8 10.3-16.5 18-16.5S46.8 43.2 50 54\" class=\"face-body\"\/>\n              <\/svg>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"viora-reviewer-info\">\n              <strong>J. L.<\/strong>\n              <span>Early taster<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n          <div class=\"viora-tasted-date\">Tasted on May 12, 2026<\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/article>\n\n      <article class=\"viora-testimonial-card\">\n        <div class=\"viora-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n\n        <p class=\"viora-quote\">\n          “Lightly sweet, rich, and actually satisfying. I would eat this every morning.”\n        <\/p>\n\n        <div class=\"viora-review-footer\">\n          <div class=\"viora-reviewer\">\n            <div class=\"viora-face-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\">\n                <circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"32\" class=\"face-bg\"\/>\n                <circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"24\" r=\"9.5\" class=\"face-head\"\/>\n                <path d=\"M14 54c3.2-10.8 10.3-16.5 18-16.5S46.8 43.2 50 54\" class=\"face-body\"\/>\n              <\/svg>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"viora-reviewer-info\">\n              <strong>M. T.<\/strong>\n              <span>Early taster<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n          <div class=\"viora-tasted-date\">Tasted on May 14, 2026<\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/article>\n\n      <article class=\"viora-testimonial-card\">\n        <div class=\"viora-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n\n        <p class=\"viora-quote\">\n          “It tastes clean and balanced, but still creamy enough to feel premium.”\n        <\/p>\n\n        <div class=\"viora-review-footer\">\n          <div class=\"viora-reviewer\">\n            <div class=\"viora-face-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\">\n                <circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"32\" class=\"face-bg\"\/>\n                <circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"24\" r=\"9.5\" class=\"face-head\"\/>\n                <path d=\"M14 54c3.2-10.8 10.3-16.5 18-16.5S46.8 43.2 50 54\" class=\"face-body\"\/>\n              <\/svg>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"viora-reviewer-info\">\n              <strong>S. K.<\/strong>\n              <span>Early taster<\/span>\n            <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n          <div class=\"viora-tasted-date\">Tasted on May 16, 2026<\/div>\n        <\/div>\n      <\/article>\n\n      <article class=\"viora-testimonial-card\">\n        <div class=\"viora-stars\">★★★★★<\/div>\n\n        <p class=\"viora-quote\">\n          “The texture is the best part. Smooth, thick, and not too sweet.”\n        <\/p>\n\n        <div class=\"viora-review-footer\">\n          <div class=\"viora-reviewer\">\n            <div class=\"viora-face-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <svg